Author: LuluTheLoli
Text: i’ve talked to her about it before, she’s just not super big on the getting outside help thing. thank you <33.

Author: intertropical
Text: she def sounds like she cares about you a great deal and is super concerned :( and I know these things are a bitch to talk about but maybe you could tell her what you're going through? she can help you get the support and resources you need – and you absolutely deserve to feel better and get better and love yourself, no matter how much you ate (or will eat). sending love <3
